vlib_kalmanFilter_2x4_S16_F32 Struct Reference

#include <VLIB_kalmanFilter.h>

Detailed Description

Structure defining the state of the Kalman filter for the S16_F32, 2x4 (2-Dimension Observation x 4-Dimension State Vectors) variant.
